race.comment: RAPID ON FIRE (5) won comfortably last time scoring by 4.5 lengths at this track after jumping from box 8 (21.68). Will need some luck early after drawing a tricky box here. Can continue the winning form. DONE AND DUSTED (1) has been in the money at his last two runs, most recently when third beaten 4 lengths (20.13). Well placed and gets his chance. MESSY IN HEAVEN (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 352m behind King Roger (20.33) in a Grade 4/5. Was a winner prior to that. Won at his only start from this draw. One of the main contenders. MONKEY PANTS (3) placed here at this trip last start - cannot be ignored.
